import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { AdminService } from '../admin.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-view-customers', templateUrl: './view-customers.component.html', styleUrls: ['./view-customers.component.css'] }) export class ViewCustomersComponent { users:any constructor(private viewService:AdminService) { } ngOnInit() { this.viewService.GetCustomers() .subscribe(response => { this.users = response; console.log(response); }); } }
